        <updateDate>2019-11-29T13:12:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Maximum Incarceration for Terrorists Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes certain federal prisoners ineligible to receive good time credit.</p> <p>Specifically, it prohibits good time credit for a federal prisoner who is serving time for certain terrorism offenses.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
